{"id":55796,"title":"Fibrotic encapsulation of a dexamethasone intravitreal implant following vitrectomy and silicone oil for rhegmatogenous retinal detachment.","abstract":"Steroids are commonly used as adjunct therapy in the management of proliferative vitreoretinopathy. The authors report a case of proliferative vitreoretinopathy treated with an intravitreal dexamethasone implant following vitrectomy in a silicone oil-filled eye. Epiretinal fibrosis developed around the implant at 6 weeks postoperatively, resulting in a recurrent retinal detachment. This was repaired by vitrectomy, removal of the implant, and peeling of epiretinal proliferation.","date":"2014-06-04","categories":"Eye Diseases","split":"test","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24806700","annotations":[{"name":"Retinal detachment","weight":0.886534,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Retinal_detachment"},{"name":"Silicone","weight":0.654166,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Silicone"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.558353,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Human eye","weight":0.545423,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Human_eye"},{"name":"Steroid","weight":0.471167,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Steroid"},{"name":"Fibrosis","weight":0.21478,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fibrosis"},{"name":"Cell growth","weight":0.144383,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cell_growth"},{"name":"Retinal","weight":0.115795,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Retinal"},{"name":"Dexamethasone","weight":0.113142,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dexamethasone"},{"name":"Oil","weight":0.0318302,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oil"},{"name":"Silicone oil","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Silicone_oil"},{"name":"Implant (medicine)","weight":0.0297435,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Implant_(medicine)"},{"name":"Vitrectomy","weight":0.0287296,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vitrectomy"},{"name":"Detachment","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Detachment"},{"name":"Intravitreal administration","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Intravitreal_administration"},{"name":"Epiretinal membrane","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Epiretinal_membrane"},{"name":"Professor","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Professor"},{"name":"Management","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Management"}]}
